name: ANALYSIS OF NEET 2024 EXAMINATION DISCREPANCIES
desc: Conducted an in-depth data analysis on the 2024 NEET examination to investigate reported discrepancies and anomalies. Using Python, I processed and analyzed a dataset of approximately 2.3 million records, focusing on data cleaning, anomaly detection, and visualization with libraries like Pandas, Matplotlib, and Seaborn
